 within about 200 yds of destin when come down from line . Carriag telescop one this chap was in was smash to piec injur him , also all his platoon except 7 or 8. Temperatur much milder all snow thaw away make place veri sloppi . Met Bob Clark who came down from No 59 2 day ago . Had supper with him . 11/1/18 Saw French airship . Milder temperatur . Had coupl rout march . Had supper with Bob Clark . 12/1/18 Read letter from Mr Randal . Rain all morn . After dinner went down to Boulogn for 4 or 5 hour had tea down there ? steak , chip coffe cost 2fr 2.
